{"word":"Shammah","slug":"shammah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shammah</b> <a href=\"#/H8048\">H8048</a> <br/> 1. Son of Reuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=13'>Gen 36:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=17'>Gen 36:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=37'>1Ch 1:37</a><br/> 2. David's brother<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=9'>1Sa 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=13'>1Sa 17:13</a> <br/> - Called Shimeah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=3'>2Sa 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=32'>2Sa 13:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=21'>2Sa 21:21</a> <br/> - Called Shimma<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=13'>1Ch 2:13</a> <br/> - Called Shimea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=7'>1Ch 20:7</a> <br/> 3. One of David's mighty men, son of Agee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=12'>2Sa 23:12</a><br/> 4. One of David's mighty men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=25'>2Sa 23:25</a><br/> - Called Shammoth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=27'>1Ch 11:27</a> <br/> 5. A Hararite, one of David's mighty men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=33'>2Sa 23:33</a>"}]}